  "text": "Migration of DC was measured in 24-well transwell culture chambers (Costar, Cambridge, MA, US) as previously described [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . The 8 μm-pore transwell filters were briefly coated with 10 μg/cm 2 fibronectin (Sigma). The upper chamber compartment was loaded with 2.5 × 10 5 IFN-DC or IL-4/TNF-DC in 150 μl X-VIVO 20 medium. The lower chamber compartment was filled with 500 μl medium supplemented with 100 ng/ml recombinant Mip-3β (Promocell, Heidelberg, Germany). After 2 h incubation at 37°C, cells were harvested from the lower chamber compartment and counted by FACS analysis using BD calibration beads.",
